com.skratchdot.riff.wav

Interface ChunkUnknown

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Chunk
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChunkUnknownImpl

    public interface ChunkUnknown
extends Chunk
    A representation of the model object 'Chunk Unknown'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Data
    • Unknown Chunk Type Id Value
    • Wav Random Access File Pointer

    See Also:
    WavPackage.getChunkUnknown()
